query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 0 AND propertyType = 'apartment' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as studios,
  SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as one_bedroom,
  SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as two_bedroom,
  SUM(CASE WHEN bedrooms >= 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as three_plus_bedroom,
  SUM(CASE WHEN propertyType = 'commercial' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as parking,
  MIN(price) as min_price,
  MAX(price) as max_price
FROM properties 
WHERE title LIKE 'Ambassadori Island%';
